place.name: KEIG
place.gazetteerText: Keig, par., mid. Aberdeenshire, on river Don, 8059 ac., pop. 776; P.O.; in S. of par. is Whitehouse sta., 2¾ miles SE. of Alford. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
